CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

March 4, 2014

[Cite as 03/04/2014 Case Announcements, 2014-Ohio-774.]

DISCIPLINARY CASES

2014-0136. Lorain Cty. Bar Assn. v. Johnson.

This matter came on for further consideration upon the filing of a motion in support of interim default suspension by relator, Lorain County Bar Association, on February 12, 2014.

Upon consideration thereof, it is ordered by the court that relator’s motion is dismissed as moot.
